[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">“I love this banking app! No fees for overdraft, I get paid 2 days earlier. If I could give it more than 5 stars, I would.”</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-row justify-between"><div class="flex flex-row gap-2 text-[16px]"><div data-contentful-field-id="cta" data-contentful-entry-id="6Uvjvv8FUCc4wlirM4Q6Uc"><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details/Chime_Mobile_Banking?id=com.onedebit.chime&amp;hl=en_SG" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit hover:text-accent-grey-500 active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer no-underline text-[size:inherit] font-sans font-medium">Play Store</a></div><div class="relative w-[20px] h-[20px]" data-contentful-field-id="media" data-contentful-entry-id="6Uvjvv8FUCc4wlirM4Q6Uc"><img alt="Google Play logo." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-contain" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="20px" srcSet="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/72BZzzSPrkSAbh1hPUdMwT/62113e3cc6e7954bc5f8da59b4146b58/google-play-logo__1_.svg?w=32&amp;h=34&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 32w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/72BZzzSPrkSAbh1hPUdMwT/62113e3cc6e7954bc5f8da59b4146b58/google-play-logo__1_.svg?w=48&amp;h=51&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 48w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/72BZzzSPrkSAbh1hPUdMwT/62113e3cc6e7954bc5f8da59b4146b58/google-play-logo__1_.svg?w=64&amp;h=68&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 64w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/72BZzzSPrkSAbh1hPUdMwT/62113e3cc6e7954bc5f8da59b4146b58/google-play-logo__1_.svg?w=96&amp;h=102&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 96w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/72BZzzSPrkSAbh1hPUdMwT/62113e3cc6e7954bc5f8da59b4146b58/google-play-logo__1_.svg?w=128&amp;h=136&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 128w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/72BZzzSPrkSAbh1hPUdMwT/62113e3cc6e7954bc5f8da59b4146b58/google-play-logo__1_