KWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=750&amp;h=750&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 750w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3PafdtRKWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=828&amp;h=828&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 828w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3PafdtRKWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1080&amp;h=1080&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1080w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3PafdtRKWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1200&amp;h=1200&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1200w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3PafdtRKWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1920&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1920w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3PafdtRKWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=2048&amp;h=2048&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 2048w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3PafdtRKWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=3840&amp;h=3840&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 3840w" src="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3PafdtRKWnhWOfi2BQspNd/14fb309c35da607f9ec96f6c05cb5b21/Sign_up.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=3840&amp;h=3840&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50"/></div></div><div class="flex flex-col w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:mt-6  sm:justify-end"><div class="empty:hidden mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-grey-200 in-cw-dark-colorways:text-lettuce max-sm:mx-auto"><div data-contentful-field-id="eyebrow" data-contentful-entry-id="2HvufNJ8BoNRZJnbvyj0iC" data-testid="eyebrow-alternate-logo"><img alt="Chime logo. " loading="lazy" width="72" height="21" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="object-cover rounded-none" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/yotdxJL87qeGLqgbdb678/29b00551376d6a7ba307dc4a042c1dd1/chime_logo.svg?w=96&amp;h=28&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1x, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/yotdxJL87qeGLqgbdb678/29b00551376d6a7ba307dc4a042c1dd1/chime_logo.svg?w=256&amp;h=75&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 2x" src="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/yotdxJL87qeGLqgbdb678/29b00551376d6a7ba307dc4a042c1dd1/chime_logo.svg?w=256&amp;h=75&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50"/></div></div><div class="font-sans font-semibold sm:w-full text-heading-md md:text-heading-lg leading-none" data-contentful-field-id="headline" data-contentful-entry-id="2HvufNJ8BoNRZJnbvyj0iC"><h2 class="group">Open a Chime checking account in minutes.</h2></div><div class="font-serif font-body-serif text-lg mt-6"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Download now to get started.</p></div><div class="empty:hidden mt-8 md:mt-[50px]"><div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-5 max-sm:justify-center"><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/chime-mobile-banking/id836215269" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit hover:text-accent-grey-500 active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer no-underline text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset)"><img alt="Apple App Store button." loading="lazy" width="182.72727272727272" height="40" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="object-cover rounded-none" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/2thvMa9anCij8hUA2QNiA5/e150c4820e6e316d53104cd146eda523/Apple_App_Store.svg?w=256&amp;h=56&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1x, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/2thvMa9anCij8hUA2QNiA5/e150c4820e6e316d53104cd146eda523/Apple_App_Store.svg?w=384&amp;h=84&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 2x" src="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/2thvMa9anCij8hUA2QNiA5/e150c4820e6e316d53104cd146eda523/Apple_App_Store.svg?w=384&amp;h=84&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50"/></a><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onedebit.chime&amp;hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit hover:text-accent-grey-500 active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer no-underline text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset)"><img alt="Google Play logo" loading="lazy" width="182.72727272727272" height="40" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="object-cover rounded-none" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/24yXLbQxRjl3VV8X34b4rI/fc9d0a17ad1d71b44c9f5b79c1338570/Google_Play.svg?w=256&amp;h=56&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1x, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/24yXLbQxRjl3VV8X34b4rI/fc9d0a17ad1d71b44c9f5b79c1338570/Google_Play.svg?w=384&amp;h=84&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 2x" src="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/24yXLbQxRjl3VV8X34b4rI/fc9d0a17ad1d71b44c9f5b79c1338570/Google_Play.svg?w=384&amp;h=84&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div data-module-index="7"><section id="faqs" class="all-margins white-colorway"><script class="optanon-category-C0001" type="application/ld+json" data-testid="seoMetadataSchema">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Chime an online bank?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Chime is not a bank, but a financial technology company. We partner with The Bancorp Bank, N.A. and Stride Bank, N.A., Members FDIC, which are both FDIC-insured."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do you open an account online through Chime?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Apply in minutes on chime.com or download the Chime mobile app (Google Play or Apple App Store).You must be at least 18 years old, and you’ll need your Social Security number, email address, and a valid U.S. address.Set Up Banking Once approved, you can connect your existing bank account to transfer funds or set up direct deposit. You can access your account anytime via the mobile app or at chime.com.Receive Your Virtual Debit Card After enrollment, you can add your virtual debit card to your wallet. If you would like a physical card, you can request one in the app. Read our blog for more information on how to open up your account through Chime, manage your money with our mobile app, and take advantage of our user-friendly features."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Where can I find a fee-free ATM?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Chime has access to more than   nationwide at stores like Walgreens®, 7-Eleven®, CVS Pharmacy®, and Circle K. You can find Chime ATMs in the app or with the ATM Finder on Chime’s website."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does Chime require a credit check to open an account online?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Chime does not require a credit check to open an online account. We provide services that are inclusive of all Americans. This includes those who struggle with bad credit history but are still looking for checking or savings accounts they can open and use entirely online with no opening deposit required."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What banks partner with Chime?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Chime is a financial technology company that offers banking services through two banking partners: The Bancorp Bank, N.A. and Stride Bank, N.A., Members FDIC. Because Chime partners with these banks, your funds are FDIC-insured through The Bancorp Bank, N.A., or Stride Bank, N.A.§"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I deposit money into my Chime account?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"When you sign up for Chime, you can easily move money into your account online. Just link an external bank account to set up a transfer. To continue to get money in your Chime account, set up direct deposit from your employer or payroll provider.  You can deposit cash into your Chime Account at over  retail locations with our cash deposit partners. The retailer that receives your cash will be responsible to transfer the funds for deposit into your Chime Account.  Still have questions? Read our full guide on how to move money into Chime."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Are Chime Account Deposits FDIC insured?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Your funds are insured up to the standard maximum deposit insurance amount of up to $250,000 through our partner banks, Stride Bank, N.A. or The Bancorp Bank, N.A., Members FDIC.§ Chime itself is not FDIC-insured; The Bancorp Bank, N.A. and Stride Bank, N.A. are the FDIC-insured members. Deposit insurance covers the failure of an insured bank. Certain conditions must be satisfied for pass-through deposit insurance coverage to apply."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Where can I go to add money to my Chime debit card?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"You can add money to your Chime Checking Account by making a fee-free cash deposit at any Walgreens location nationwide. And it’s not just Walgreens – for a fee, you can deposit cash into your Chime account at more than  retailers across the country.You can also fund your debit card with direct deposit, mobile check deposit, instant transfers, and bank transfers, all in the mobile app."}}]}</script><div class="content-wrapper"><div class="font-sans font-semibold text-heading-md md:text-heading-lg" data-contentful-field-id="headline" data-contentful-entry-id="7Ff30r2YHT59De7nuYnL9Q"><h2 class="group">FAQs</h2></div><div class="mt-6 md:mt-14"><div><div class="panel mt-6 md:mt-14" id="panel-" data-contentful-field-id="content" data-contentful-entry-id="4OoR884MoZClUi4nZycsJE"><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="63AR8trPcjNbK8HwYQnNyL"><h3 class="group h3">Is Chime an online bank?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="63AR8trPcjNbK8HwYQnNyL"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Chime is not a bank, but a financial technology company. We partner with The Bancorp Bank, N.A. and Stride Bank, N.A., Members FDIC, which are both FDIC-insured.</p></div></details></div><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="VHiFEBXXlmxwTu2edSp6v"><h3 class="group h3">How do you open an account online through Chime?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="VHiFEBXXlmxwTu2edSp6v"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Apply in minutes on chime.com or download the Chime mobile app (<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.onedebit.chime&amp;hl=en_US" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset) inline underline hover:text-(--richtext-link-hover) focus:text-(--richtext-link-hover)" data-testid="inline-hyperlink">Google Play</a> or <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/chime-mobile-banking/id836215269" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset) inline underline hover:text-(--richtext-link-hover) focus:text-(--richtext-link-hover)" data-testid="inline-hyperlink">Apple App Store</a>).</p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">You must be at least 18 years old, and you’ll need your Social Security number, email address, and a valid U.S. address.</p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Set Up Banking </p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Once approved, you can connect your existing bank account to transfer funds or set up direct deposit. You can access your account anytime via the mobile app or at chime.com.</p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Receive Your Virtual Debit Card </p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">After enrollment, you can add your virtual debit card to your wallet. If you would like a physical card, you can request one in the app. </p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Read our <a href="https://www.chime.com/blog/" class="items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset) inline underline hover:text-(--richtext-link-hover) focus:text-(--richtext-link-hover)" data-testid="inline-hyperlink">blog</a> for more information on how to open up your account through Chime, manage your money with our mobile app, and take advantage of our user-friendly features.</p></div></details></div><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="6OYbq8ptwq70UtVj8BPLyH"><h3 class="group h3">Where can I find a fee-free ATM?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="6OYbq8ptwq70UtVj8BPLyH"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Chime has access to more than <span data-testid="inline-richtext"><a href="https://www.chime.com/blog/how-to-find-an-atm-near-me-for-chime/" class="items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit hover:text-accent-grey-500 active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset) inline underline" data-testid="inline-hyperlink">47,000 fee-free ATMs</a></span><span class="font-inherit"><sup>2</sup></span>  nationwide at stores like Walgreens<sup class="superscript-small">®</sup>, 7-Eleven<sup class="superscript-small">®</sup>, CVS Pharmacy<sup class="superscript-small">®</sup>, and Circle K. You can find Chime ATMs in the app or with the <a href="/online-banking/atms/" class="items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset) inline underline hover:text-(--richtext-link-hover) focus:text-(--richtext-link-hover)" data-testid="entry-hyperlink">ATM Finder</a> on Chime’s website.</p></div></details></div><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="5Gt8b6u5CuEHbtL7a5Erld"><h3 class="group h3">Does Chime require a credit check to open an account online?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="5Gt8b6u5CuEHbtL7a5Erld"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Chime does not require a credit check to open an online account. We provide services that are inclusive of all Americans. This includes those who struggle with bad credit history but are still looking for checking or savings accounts they can open and use entirely online with no opening deposit required.</p></div></details></div><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="5we4kejJX6Qay51bEPWMbb"><h3 class="group h3">What banks partner with Chime?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="5we4kejJX6Qay51bEPWMbb"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Chime is a financial technology company that offers banking services through two banking partners: The Bancorp Bank, N.A. and Stride Bank, N.A., Members FDIC. Because Chime partners with these banks, your funds are FDIC-insured through The Bancorp Bank, N.A., or Stride Bank, N.A.<sup class="superscript-tall">§</sup></p></div></details></div><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="js0YNWDcI7T3kE78wx6Dm"><h3 class="group h3">How do I deposit money into my Chime account?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="js0YNWDcI7T3kE78wx6Dm"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">When you sign up for Chime, you can easily move money into your account online. Just link an external bank account to set up a transfer. To continue to get money in your Chime account, set up direct deposit from your employer or payroll provider.  </p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">You can deposit cash<span class="font-inherit"><sup>13</sup></span> into your Chime Account at over <span data-testid="inline-richtext">100,000</span> retail locations with our cash deposit partners. The retailer that receives your cash will be responsible to transfer the funds for deposit into your Chime Account.  </p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Still have questions? Read our <a href="https://www.chime.com/blog/how-to-move-money-into-chime/" class="items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer text-[size:inherit] font-(--link-weight-reset) inline underline hover:text-(--richtext-link-hover) focus:text-(--richtext-link-hover)" data-testid="inline-hyperlink">full guide</a> on how to move money into Chime.</p></div></details></div><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="7qok8r2c7JK5PsxrMtVSa0"><h3 class="group h3">Are Chime Account Deposits FDIC insured?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="7qok8r2c7JK5PsxrMtVSa0"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">Your funds are insured up to the standard maximum deposit insurance amount of up to $250,000 through our partner banks, Stride Bank, N.A. or The Bancorp Bank, N.A., Members FDIC.<sup class="superscript-tall">§</sup> <!-- -->Chime itself is not FDIC-insured; The Bancorp Bank, N.A. and Stride Bank, N.A. are the FDIC-insured members. Deposit insurance covers the failure of an insured bank. Certain conditions must be satisfied for pass-through deposit insurance coverage to apply.</p></div></details></div><div class=""><div class="border-t border-primary"></div><details class="py-4 flex flex-col group open:mb-2 px-6 open:p-6 md:open:-mx-6 md:px-0 open:[&amp;_td]:text-[unset] open:rounded-md open:dark-green-colorway"><summary class="font-sans font-medium list-none flex justify-between items-center gap-3 max-sm:text-body-saans text-heading-sm cursor-pointer" data-contentful-field-id="accordionLabelRte" data-contentful-entry-id="3euGT3jZd4JKp6F9BidU1s"><h3 class="group h3">Where can I go to add money to my Chime debit card?</h3><span><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="group-open:hidden"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect><rect x="12.75" y="2" width="20" height="1.5" transform="rotate(90 12.75 2)" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden group-open:block"><rect x="2" y="11" width="20" height="1.5" fill="currentColor"></rect></svg></span></summary><div class="pt-6 font-serif text-body-serif" data-contentful-field-id="accordionCopy" data-contentful-entry-id="3euGT3jZd4JKp6F9BidU1s"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">You can add money to your Chime Checking Account by making a fee-free cash deposit at any Walgreens location nationwide. And it’s not just Walgreens – for a fee, you can deposit cash into your Chime account at more than <span data-testid="inline-richtext">85,000</span> retailers across the country.</p><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">You can also fund your debit card with direct deposit, mobile check deposit,<span class="font-inherit"><sup>14</sup></span> instant transfers,<span class="font-inherit"><sup>15</sup></span> and bank transfers, all in the mobile app.</p></div></details></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><div data-module-index="8"><section class="flex dark-green-colorway h-[494px] sm:h-[744px]" id="mission"><picture data-testid="responsive-image"><source srcSet="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=640&amp;h=811&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 640w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=750&amp;h=950&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 750w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=828&amp;h=1049&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 828w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1080&amp;h=1368&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1080w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1200&amp;h=1520&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1200w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1920&amp;h=2433&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1920w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=2048&amp;h=2595&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 2048w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/3dPlUjkrmJsksvjoDMDuus/d94e8a9d26ddb3ecb345880b2dc29246/chime_member_mobile.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=3157&amp;h=4000&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 3840w" media="(max-width: 750px)" sizes="100vw"/><source srcSet="/_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=640&amp;h=331&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 640w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=750&amp;h=387&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 750w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=828&amp;h=428&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 828w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1080&amp;h=558&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1080w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1200&amp;h=620&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1200w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=1920&amp;h=992&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 1920w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=2048&amp;h=1058&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 2048w, /_ctf-img/ao7gxs2zk32d/1kTPPw8pguEvd6fCJeDfTe/d0e10f1cc0671609612c6cff9bcae2d1/chime-members-hp.webp?fm=webp&amp;w=3840&amp;h=1984&amp;fit=fill&amp;q=50 3840w" media="(min-width: 751px)" sizes="100vw"/><img width="3871" height="2000" style="color:transparent" alt="Nine different Chime members sitting and standing around a green couch with the Chime logo in the background." class="object-cover absolute rounded-none w-full object-top h-[494px] sm:h-[744px]" loading="lazy"/></picture><div class="content-wrapper z-10 relative h-full flex flex-col text-center justify-end font-sans leading-[1.12] py-8.5 sm:py-16"><div class="text-fern text-label-saans" data-contentful-field-id="eyebrow" data-contentful-entry-id="5M3b31z88pSQq3MV5uiWlJ"><div class="empty:hidden mb-4"><div class="text-eyebrow font-sans" data-contentful-field-id="eyebrowText" data-contentful-entry-id="5M3b31z88pSQq3MV5uiWlJ" data-testid="eyebrow-text"><p class="peer paragraph peer-[.paragraph]:my-4 last:mb-0">CHIME MEMBERS</p></div></div></div><div class="font-semibold text-heading-md sm:text-heading-xl" data-contentful-field-id="headline" data-contentful-entry-id="5M3b31z88pSQq3MV5uiWlJ"><h3 class="group h3">Our mission is to unite everyday people to unlock their financial progress.</h3></div></div></section></div></div></div></main><footer data-theme="www" data-footer="true" class="py-[44px] sm:py-[88px] md:py-[97px] darkest-green-colorway"><div data-module-index="1"><div class="content-wrapper" data-testid="site-footer"><div class="keyline hidden"><div class="pt-1"><div class="border-t border-(--keyline-color)" data-testid="keyline"></div></div></div><section class="footer-section pb-8 sm:pb-12 flex flex-col sm:grid sm:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-16 sm:gap-12 justify-between " data-testid="footer" data-contentful-field-id="footerColumns" data-contentful-entry-id="4tpPw8hxOFkYeodjtZkOgk"><div class="flex flex-col gap-2" data-testid="footerCol"><p class="font-bold mb-2 font-sans">Popular Features</p><a href="/online-banking/chime-membership-tiers/" target="_self" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer no-underline text-[size:inherit] hover:text-fern focus:text-fern font-sans font-medium" data-testid="footerColumnLink">Membership Tiers</a><a href="https://www.chime.com/online-banking/debit-card/" target="_self" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-label origin-center transition-all underline-offset-[3px] w-fit active:bg-shade-primary-100 active:rounded-none active:text-accent-grey-500 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer no-underline text-[size:inherit] hover:text-fern focus:text-fern font-sans font-medium" data-testid="footerColumnLink">Chime Debit Card</a><a href="https://www.chime.com/credit/credit-builder/" targe