k ATM withdrawal and over the counter advance fees may apply except at FCTI\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"value\":\"®\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" ATMs in a 7-Eleven\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"value\":\"®\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" or Speedway, or any Allpoint\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"value\":\"®\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" or Visa\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"value\":\"®\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" Plus Alliance ATM participating in the Allpoint network.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"1I9QLTYO2Tk1LMWDrvrue8\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"SpotMe\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"value\":\"®\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" on Credit is an optional, no interest/no fee overdraft line of credit tied to the Secured Deposit Account. SpotMe on Debit is an optional, no fee service attached to your Chime Checking Account (individually or collectively, \\\"SpotMe\\\"). Eligibility for SpotMe requires $200 or more in qualifying direct deposits to your Chime Checking Account each month. \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Qualifying members will be allowed to overdraw their Chime Checking Account and/or their Secured Deposit Account up to $20 in total, but may be later eligible for a higher combined limit of up to $200 or more based on member’s Chime account history, direct deposit frequency and amount, spending activity and other risk-based factors. Your SpotMe Limit will be displayed to you within the Chime mobile app. You will receive notice of any changes to your SpotMe Limit. SpotMe for Credit and SpotMe on Debit share a single SpotMe limit. Your SpotMe Limit may change at any time, at Chime or its banking partners’ discretion. Although there are no overdraft fees, there may be out-of-network or third-party fees associated with ATM transactions or OTC cash withdrawal fees at retailers. SpotMe won’t cover non-card transactions, including ACH transfers, Pay Anyone transfers, or Chime Checkbook transactions. \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/\"},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"SpotMe terms and conditions\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\".\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"16MJnDGk0Rk1S7M9oJuKsS\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"With qualifying direct deposits, earn \",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"embedded-entry-inline\",\"data\":{\"target\":{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"55N0w3tQuNG8MyWnL9OnnR\"}}},\"content\":[]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" cash back as a Chime Prime member or \",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"embedded-entry-inline\",\"data\":{\"target\":{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"edwgdkqON7och3Pj9gAZA\"}}},\"content\":[]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" cash back as a Chime Plus member on up to $1,500 of eligible secured Chime Visa\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"®\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" Credit Card purchases. See the \",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\",\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/chime-card-cash-rewards-addendum-prime-beta/\"},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Secured Chime Visa\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\",\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/chime-card-cash-rewards-addendum-prime-beta/\"},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"®\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"data\":{}}]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\",\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/chime-card-cash-rewards-addendum-prime/\"},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" Credit Card - Cash Rewards Program Addendum\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" for limitations and details on earning cash back on your monthly selected category.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"55N0w3tQuNG8MyWnL9OnnR\"},\"__typename\":\"Shortcode\",\"shortCodeValue\":{\"json\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"5%\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]}}},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"edwgdkqON7och3Pj9gAZA\"},\"__typename\":\"Shortcode\",\"shortCodeValue\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"2%\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"}}}]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"2Wc654sIujRyAc5EE1bngU\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Out-of-network ATM withdrawal and OTC advance fees may apply. View The \",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\",\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/bancorp/chime-card-agreement/\"},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Bancorp agreement\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" or \",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\",\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/stride/chime-card-agreement/\"},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Stride agreement\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" for details; see back of card for issuer.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"32C5zT0J7unZhitKcJ08u5\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"The 3.75% Annual Percentage Yield (APY) is only available to members with Chime Prime status, otherwise, either the 3.00% APY for members with Chime Plus status or the standard rate of 0.75% APY will apply. The APYs are effective as of 04/02/2026, are variable and may change at any time. No minimum balance required. Must have $0.01 in savings to earn interest. See \",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\",\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/chime-membership-tiers-prime/\"},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Chime Membership Tiers Terms and Conditions\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\" for more details.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"2C16DneQjyN3ZcQkHxF3mu\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Round Ups automatically round up debit card and credit card purchases to the nearest dollar and transfers the round up into your savings account. You can also automatically transfer part of your direct deposits of $1 or more from your Checking Account into your selected Chime account(s).\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"4e2YE0ypjjKifJqY0BoeXM\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Some restrictions apply. To be eligible for MyPay\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"superscript\"}],\"value\":\"®\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\", you must receive qualifying direct deposits to your Chime Checking Account in the preceding 36 days as set forth in the MyPay Agreement. A Qualifying Direct Deposit is a deposit from an employer, payroll provider, gig economy payer, government benefits payer, or other permitted source of income by Automated Clearing House (“ACH”) or Original Credit Transaction (“OCT”). Your MyPay Credit Limit and Maximum Available Advance may change at any time. MyPay is a line of credit and available limits are based on estimated income and risk-based criteria. Eligible members may be offered a $20 - $500 Credit Limit per pay period. Limits may be impacted by your use of other Chime products. Your Credit Limit and Maximum Available Advance will be displayed to you within the Chime app. MyPay is currently only available to eligible Chime members in certain states. Other restrictions may apply. \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"See \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/bancorp/mypay/\"},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Bancorp MyPay Agreement\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" or \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/stride/mypay/\"},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Stride MyPay Agreement\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" for details.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"1xPRaKCaGtItk121kBnUB7\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Early access to direct deposit funds depends on the timing of the submission of the payment file from the payer. We generally make these funds available on the day the payment file is received, which may be up to 2 days earlier than the scheduled payment date.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"5ctF7nctNRPGnjdjn2xFsF\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Option to get funds instantly for a fee of 3% of the advance amount ($2 minimum, $5 maximum) per advance, or get funds for free within 24 hours. See \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/bancorp/mypay/\"},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Bancorp MyPay Agreement\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" or \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"},{\"data\":{\"uri\":\"https://www.chime.com/policies/stride/mypay/\"},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Stride MyPay Agreement\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"hyperlink\"},{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\" for details.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"5zdp0DRzczKN8s5Pqg9unH\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"You must notify your financial institution immediately of any unauthorized use. For specific restrictions, limitations and other details, please consult your issuer.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"3VkmWRvF9YvyZry5m3SMRz\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Based on 2025 internal comparison to select traditional bank and fintech offerings. \",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"THE MOST REWARDING WAY TO BANK is a Trademark of Chime Financial, Inc.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"2xBnbBvcp2pQRoAWQUchNN\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Once the retailer accepts your cash, the funds will be transferred to your Chime account. You may use your barcode, debit card, or Chime Card to deposit cash. Cash deposit fees may apply if using a retailer other than Walgreens and Duane Reade. Cash deposits using a barcode or debit card are deposited to your Checking Account. If you have the Chime Card, those funds will be automatically swept to your Chime Card Secured Deposit Account. Cash deposits using your Chime Card first go to your Chime Card Account, then transferred to your Chime Card Secured Deposit Account. Cash deposits are not payment for any Chime Card balance due.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"1iRB3Tvb2rMbS5VxUq31RF\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Mobile Check Deposit eligibility is determined by Chime in its sole discretion and may be granted based on various factors including, but not limited to, a member's direct deposit enrollment status.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1},{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"K5qJUtxU5qExOFUSoqMZ4\"},\"symbol\":null,\"copy\":{\"json\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"There may be times when instant transfers may be delayed due to network timing or other factors beyond our control.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"links\":{\"entries\":{\"inline\":[]}}},\"moduleIndex\":1}],\"children\":[\"$L75\",\"$L76\",false,false,\"$L77\"]}]}]\n"])</script><script nonce="ZmIwOWI5YmQtZWI3Yi00ZmVlLWFkYTgtYjM2YTdiNDA5ODM4">self.__next_f.push([1,"7a:I[27201,[\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/0v-ofcow-6~o3.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/04_2q22a2gb4i.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/0a9amd5i33j-w.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/0xo37s4asvnu0.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/00g4i7epr953q.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/0t_yyp-grsjt8.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/06o~5xt9r89tl.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/05999z0~jgm.w.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/0~9z68223-hmu.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/0jm-a-6mnlh5l.js\",\"/_assets_cdn/_next/static/chunks/02442ijzsv1w4.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n6c:[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"stroke\":\"#fff\",\"strokeMiterlimit\":10,\"strokeWidth\":0.23,\"d\":\"M53.87 11.64c0 .95-.28 1.71-.85 2.28-.64.67-1.48 1.01-2.5 1.01s-1.82-.34-2.51-1.02-1.03-1.53-1.03-2.54.34-1.86 1.03-2.54 1.52-1.02 2.51-1.02c.49 0 .96.1 1.4.29s.8.44 1.07.76l-.6.6c-.45-.54-1.07-.81-1.87-.81-.72 0-1.34.25-1.86.76-.52.5-.78 1.16-.78 1.97s.26 1.46.78 1.97c.52.5 1.14.76 1.86.76.76 0 1.4-.25 1.9-.76q.495-.495.57-1.38h-2.48v-.82h3.3c.03.18.05.35.05.51zM59.1 8.79H56v2.16h2.8v.82H56v2.16h3.1